  monica-security-modernization,related,"2026-07-16T16:59:37.486Z",null,null
comments[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-16T16:59:37.486Z",codex-root,CodeQL password-hash/logging alerts remain false positives because the API key is only SHA-256 fingerprinted for masking and never logged raw.
notes[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-16T16:59:37.486Z",codex-root,Use chmod only on non-Windows platforms and isolate permission helpers for testing.
learnings[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-16T16:59:37.486Z",codex-root,Secure creation flags are insufficient when users can migrate or pre-create configuration paths.
